sequenceDiagram
    participant Trig as Update Trigger
    participant OC as Orchestrator
    participant Spec as BP / SD Service
    participant Docs as BP / SD Pages (GitHub)
    participant E as Shared Embeddings DB
    participant Portal as Documentation Portal
    actor SME

    Trig ->> OC: Refresh event
    OC ->> Spec: Dispatch refresh task
    Note over OC,Docs: Background build hits unresolvable gap — Auto-RAG exhausted, dep-graph tie, dynamic route, or cross-ref unresolved
    Spec ->> Docs: Commit page with SME-PLACEHOLDER block(s)
    Spec -->> OC: Escalation envelope (question_id, originating_page, best_guess, trail)
    OC ->> OC: Queue, dedup by topic, resolve SME from registry
    OC -->> Portal: Surface pending question + context + best guess
    SME ->> Portal: Reply with answer
    Portal ->> OC: POST /v1/sme-replies
    OC ->> Docs: Persist as new BP document
    OC ->> Spec: Patch each originating page (placeholder to SME text + link)
    OC ->> Spec: Re-index new doc + patched pages
    Spec ->> E: Refresh embeddings (domain-tagged)
    OC ->> OC: Remove from pending_sme_questions
    Note over Trig,SME: Future queries on same topic now hit enriched, grounded retrieval — page no longer shows a gap
